            . I live next door to Mr. Mayo. On the evening of the 7th of August Mrs. Mayo came to me; I went into the street, and saw the prisoner running along with the time-piece; I went and took it from him - when he got to a corner he turned and walked deliberately down a street, with it under his left arm.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I throw myself on the mercy of the Court.</p>
